<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Pinion2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Pinion,</orth> vb. to make defenceless by binding the elbows behind together: <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.2.129" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 2, 129</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 4.2.69" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 2, 69</bibl> (Dogberry says <emph>opinioned</emph>). <bibl n="shak. lr 3.7.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 7, 23</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 53</bibl>.
